data.description: The traditional floor plan features a warm and welcoming interior that is light and uplifting and contains a flow-through living/dining area. This house boasts well-maintained laminate floors in the living area. System updates include Energy Star appliances, Wi-Fi enabled thermostats and high-efficiency kitchen appliances which makes it ready to move in. Enjoy a country atmosphere in the inviting backyard equipped with a large patio and large grassy area for yard games. An ideal spot for easy summer living. Look no more. You've found excellent suburban living. Well placed in a laid-back Guadalupe County neighborhood. Convenient to the Creekside shopping center and much more !!!!!
